<item>
            <title>[LU-18882] sanity/56ib fails: setstripe error for ..../f56ib.sanity: Read-only file system</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18882</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
== sanity test 56ib: check &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;lfs find -ost INDEX_RANGE&apos;&lt;/span&gt; command ========================================================== 01:21:38 (1743556898)
striped dir -i0 -c2 -H crush /mnt/lustre/d56ib.sanity
create file /mnt/lustre/d56ib.sanity/f56ib.sanity on OST 0
lfs setstripe: setstripe error &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;/mnt/lustre/d56ib.sanity/f56ib.sanity&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: Read-only file system
 sanity test_56ib: @@@@@@ FAIL: failed to create test file /mnt/lustre/d56ib.sanity/f56ib.sanity 
  Trace dump:
  = ./../tests/test-framework.sh:7249:error()
  = sanity.sh:7139:test_56ib()
  = ./../tests/test-framework.sh:7622:run_one()
  = ./../tests/test-framework.sh:7685:run_one_logged()
  = ./../tests/test-framework.sh:7503:run_test()
  = sanity.sh:7154:main()
Dumping lctl log to /tmp/ltest-logs/sanity.test_56ib.*.1743556899.log
Dumping logs only on local client.
FAIL 56ib (5s)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;this is due to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18833&quot; title=&quot;OS_STATE_* flags not being set correctly for read-only devices&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-18833&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-18833&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; patch which doesn&apos;t wait till obdfilter.*.readonly=0 is propagated to MDT so subsequent 56ib finds OST1 unavailable&lt;/p&gt;</description>
